    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting. While it runs and drives as expected, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, and the plastic trim pieces show light scratching. Mechanically, it has been maintained but may require some minor upcoming service typical for its mileage. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for value over aesthetics.",
